for year in df:
    current_year = year['Year'].iloc[0]
    qn2= year[['CRSDepTime','ArrDelay']].copy()
    qn2[['ArrDelay']] = qn2[['ArrDelay']].applymap(lambda x: max(0, x))
    qn2['DepTimeCategory'] = pd.cut(qn2['CRSDepTime'], bins=[0, 600, 1200, 1800, 2400], labels=['0000-0600', '0601-1200', '1201-1800', '1801-0000'], include_lowest=True, right=False)
    average_delay = qn2.groupby('DepTimeCategory')['ArrDelay'].mean()
    plt.bar(average_delay.index, average_delay)
    plt.xlabel('Departure Time Category')
    plt.ylabel('Average Delay')
    plt.title(f'Average Delay for Each Departure Time Category -{current_year}')
    plt.show()

find probability of delay (proportion)¶

In [8]:
for year in df:
    current_year = year['Year'].iloc[0]
    qn2ai = year[['Year','DayOfWeek','ArrDelay']].copy()  
    total_delayed_flights = qn2ai[qn2ai['ArrDelay'] > 15]['ArrDelay'].count()
    delayed_flights_per_day = qn2ai[qn2ai['ArrDelay'] > 15].groupby('DayOfWeek').size()
    probabilities = delayed_flights_per_day / total_delayed_flights
    
    # Plotting
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    probabilities.plot(kind='bar', color='skyblue')
    plt.title(f'Probability of Delay > 15 minutes for Each Day of the Week ({current_year})')
    plt.xlabel('Day of the Week')
    plt.ylabel('Probability')
    plt.ylim(0, 0.4)  # Set y-axis limit from 0 to 0.4
    plt.xticks(rotation=0)
    plt.grid(axis='y', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()
In [9]:
for year in df:
    current_year = year['Year'].iloc[0]
    qn2 = year[['CRSDepTime','ArrDelay']].copy()
    
    # Replace negative delay values with 0
    qn2[['ArrDelay']] = qn2[['ArrDelay']].applymap(lambda x: max(0, x))
    
    # Create Departure Time Category
    qn2['DepTimeCategory'] = pd.cut(qn2['CRSDepTime'], bins=[0, 600, 1200, 1800, 2400], 
                                    labels=['0000-0600', '0601-1200', '1201-1800', '1801-0000'], 
                                    include_lowest=True, right=False)
    
    # Calculate the total number of delayed flights for each departure time category
    total_delayed_flights = qn2[qn2['ArrDelay'] > 0].groupby('DepTimeCategory')['ArrDelay'].count()
    
    # Calculate the total number of flights for each departure time category
    total_flights_per_category = qn2.groupby('DepTimeCategory')['ArrDelay'].count()
    
    # Calculate the probability of delay for each departure time category
    probabilities = total_delayed_flights / total_flights_per_category
    
    # Plotting
    plt.bar(probabilities.index, probabilities)
    plt.xlabel('Departure Time Category')
    plt.ylabel('Probability of Delay')
    plt.title(f'Probability of Delay for Each Departure Time Category - {current_year}')
    plt.show()
